{
  "stem": "18626.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, I was going to the Talmud Torah, salient all the time. 40% of the education in Talmud Torah was Hebrew and the Bible, and Tanakh and [?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Chumash, ?] you know, all the Jewish laws, and a little Gemara.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I knew already, you know, about [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the Jewish, you know, traditions and the Judaism, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother was keeping, of course, her house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All the people in Slabodka they are kosher.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, We were with some of them, we were very friendly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it turned out when the war starts we didn't know we are not friendly.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we had very big disappointments.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because some of our friendly people who were our neighbors, came in right away to look for my father to kill him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were Lithuanians, you know, gentile people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were preparing for years, if something comes up and they start a war with Poland, and then the Russians in 1940, took Lithuania, and all the Baltic countries, you know, after that pact with Russia.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, Germany and Russia made a pact.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Russians got certain countries, like a gift, for cutting in, you know with Hitler that peace, so-called pact.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As it was, you know, later nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Lithuanians already prepare themselves with rifles and with weapons, digging in, right in their yards.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I, myself, came in one time to my father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I says, what is Mazuras, one of our neighbors, Mr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mazuras, what is he digging all the time and working in his yard?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my father says, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I hope he doesn't bury weapons there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
